Package: dedistracter
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, sqlite3, bash (>= 4.0)
Recommends: pi-hole
Description: Pi Hole v6+ distraction blocker with scheduling
 Dedistracter provides automated scheduling to block and unblock distracting
 websites using Pi Hole v6+ on a Raspberry Pi. Domains can be blocked during
 work hours and automatically unblocked during personal time.
 .
 Features:
  - Simple bash scripts for blocking/unblocking domains
  - Cron-based scheduling with configurable times
  - Environment variable configuration
  - Purpose-built for Pi Hole v6+
